It was Shredder who told Quickstrike that Megatron had left him in charge, 
not Striker. Striker is still unconcious in Rowdy Wolf's cave.

::Shredder/Prowl/Mosquitor::

Shredder looks at Quickstrike. "Your history doesn't concern me. Megatron 
left me in charge. You can take it up with him if you want."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl shakes his head. "It's ok. You needed help. I did what any maximal 
would have done."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Unable to find any predacons, Mosquitor flies back toward the predacon base.
